{"tid":354988,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"實用傳檔工具，Send by Mozilla 分享 1GB 大檔案無難度","createTime":"2017-08-11T02:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T04:52:29.000Z","uid":52675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f91614eade4a635cf32c4d2dd7adda364baa8436","tid":354988,"uid":52675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:22:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.tw/mobile/talk/102/5030760/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.tw%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F102%2F5030760%2F1%2F&d=vOTBSNjuBlgphOHGkzXh6WMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=6a7d3526\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.tw/mobile/talk/102/5030760/1/</a><br />\n說到 Firefox 大家可能會馬上想到瀏覽器，但 Firefox 的開發商 Mozilla 也有在開發其他網上服務，近期 Mozilla 就開始針對新服務「Send」進行公測。Send 是一個讓網友傳送大容量檔案的跨平台工具，傳送的檔案容量可以高達 1GB，而且完全免費也不需要註冊登記。<br />\n<img src=\"http://timg.eprice.com.tw/tw/mobile/img/2017-08/04/5030760/mansonfat_3_2a7341a6930f949a1c781698cc2f2f4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.tw%2Ftw%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2017-08%2F04%2F5030760%2Fmansonfat_3_2a7341a6930f949a1c781698cc2f2f4b.jpg&h=15f16fc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://timg.eprice.com.tw/tw/mobile/img/2017-08/04/5030760/hat7029_1_11415adf490133ea99937a1793ef0b37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.tw%2Ftw%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2017-08%2F04%2F5030760%2Fhat7029_1_11415adf490133ea99937a1793ef0b37.jpg&h=1c36bbe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n只需利用瀏覽器登入 Send 網站，就可直接開始選擇檔案並且上傳，完成上傳動作之後就可以將連結提供給接收檔案的一方。除了可以傳送高達 1GB 的大容量檔案，Send 也不需要用戶管理，只要下載一次或上傳檔案後的 24 小時，檔案就會自動從伺服器刪除。<br />\n<br />\nMozilla 表示 Send 採用客戶端保密和加密技術，所以官方也無法瀏覽用戶上載的檔案內容。儘管 Send 免費而且使用簡便，但因為屬於測試實驗性質的新服務，而且 Mozilla 日後並不一定會推出這項服務的正式版本，所以就嚐鮮試用看看就好，目前先不要把它當成主要的傳檔工具。"},{"pid":"712c3c4f09f1e57b52dacc9313925879ffa8efcb","tid":354988,"uid":28515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:48:37.000Z","msg":"咁撚費"},{"pid":"f0cd8168c9e0d3ff35ec57ebee45cd4a967ee742","tid":354988,"uid":12638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:52:33.000Z","msg":"得1gb<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa67b2a254773b212830eee76188ed6eac4ad34","tid":354988,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T04:52:29.000Z","msg":"得1GB? 日本仔隻BitSend好似無limit喎! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}